Output assets/lazytailscale.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 0

Type "./lazytailscale --demo"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Down
Sleep 500ms
Down
Sleep 500ms

Screenshot assets/lazytailscale.png

Sleep 1s
Down
Sleep 800ms
Down
Sleep 800ms
Down
Sleep 800ms

Type "p"
Sleep 4s

Up
Sleep 800ms

Type "e"
Sleep 1.5s
Type "e"
Sleep 1s

Type "?"
Sleep 2s
Type "?"
Sleep 500ms
